  "keyFeatures": [
    "Decentralized perpetual futures trading with leverage up to configurable limits",
    "Modular smart contract architecture with separate governance, order execution, and position management",
    "Liquidity provider vault system with LP tokens and fee collection mechanisms",
    "Oracle aggregation from multiple sources (Stork) with market status monitoring",
    "Order executor system for keepers to trigger and settle trades",
    "Referral program with volume-based code generation",
    "VIP scoring system for trader benefits and fee discounts",
    "Dynamic spread and funding fee mechanisms based on open interest",
    "Take profit, stop loss, and automated liquidation support",
    "Pre-deposit points system for early users"
  ],
